Full Description: Address: 343 Saratoga Rd Honolulu, HI 96815 When you find the perfect breakfast eatery, you certainly never forget it. Under the guidance of Jerry and Jan Fukunaga, a couple that believes in the importance of quality food with fresh ingredients and a dining atmosphere that treats everyone like family, Eggs 'N Things has flourished into a must-stop destination during  extended visit to Waikiki. Like other highly regarded breakfast spots, the wait for Eggs 'N Things is long, but well worth it. Guests are seated by a waiter or waitress in traditional Aloha tropical wear and offered a jaw-dropping selection of classic breakfast fare. Along with daily specials, Eggs 'N Things offers platters of meat and eggs and omelets, all of which are served with their famous buttermilk pancakes, rice, and pancakes. Guests can order Hawaii's best pancakes on their own with mouthwatering toppings, such as strawberry, banana, or blueberry whip cream, pineapples, coconuts, macadamia nuts, and chocolate chips! Enjoy these same amazing ingredients with a waffle or a crepe, if you prefer. Although Eggs 'N Things specializes in breakfast and brunch,  the restaurant also serves dinner dishes with great flourish, offering entrÃ©es such as Calamari Steak, Chicken Fried Steak, and Paniolo Loco Moco, a Waikiki classic dish. Eggs 'N Thing takes great pride in being a family restaurant, so bring the whole Ohana  along to Waikiki's favorite restaurant and enjoy irresistibly good platters of hearty breakfast.
